      "type": "verse",
      "number": "1"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The Christ we know is crucified — experience of the cross"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Allows us to enjoy His life and count ourselves but loss;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The sense of life and death within us functions as a gauge,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Equipping us to live Christ in the Body in this age."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The cross is our deliverance,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Our entrance into grace,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To deepen and increase our joy"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In Christ, His way to trace."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Draw closer to the Lord and drink the river of supply,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "With every choice and turn allowing Christ to occupy"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Our heart in all its inward parts, as open as can be,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Maintaining our enjoyment of the Lord continually."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The cross is termination,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Of all we are, the end,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The stripping off of everything"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But Christ, with God to blend."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "God’s glory in the face of Christ, His presence inwardly,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Compels us to deny the self and follow faithfully;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "As deep as His restrictions go, the riverbed is laid,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For that’s how deep the river flows, God’s life to us conveyed."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The cross is but a threshold"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "That opens up the way"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For life to flow within us deeply,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Till we’re swept away."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The churches are the house of God. His presence limits us."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "He’s standing at the gate and holds a reed to measure thus —"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Examining and testing, He is judging to possess"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Our inward being by the living flow that swallows death."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The cross brings in the river"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "That flows out from the house"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Toward God’s effulgent glory,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Like the Bride to her espoused."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "5"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "“The marriage of the Lamb has come,” will soon be heard by all,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "“His wife made herself ready,” proving naught can life forestall."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Around the bend, the Lord will come and gather up His saints,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Those ready for His coming, loving Him without constraints."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The cross is truly God’s way;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The way that we go on!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Enjoy life’s bountiful supply"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And glory in the Son!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "6"
    }
  ],
